So, now you will need to code the teleport.
In commandpackethandler and commandspackethandler, after any other command, paste that code :
[code=java]if(cmd[0].equals("nazizombie")) {
    player.sm("Welcome to the hell, kill 250 zombies and the boss for 150M!");
	player.getActionSender().removeTab1();
	if(player.SafeZone()) {
		player.getTele().telePlayer(player, 3280, 3886, 0, 0);
	} else if (Location.wildernessLevel(player.getLocation()) > 20) {
		player.sm("you cannot teleport above 20 wilderness");
	} else {
		player.getTele().telePlayer(player, 3280, 3886, 0, 0);
	}
}[/code]

So this code is the basic teleport code. You should know it.

