Now, in object1packethandler, after any break, paste this code : 
[code=java]		case 2273: //Nazi Zombies Portal
		if(player.KilledNazi >= 250) {
		player.tele(2461, 4768, 0);
		player.sm("There's the boss. If you die, you wont lose your points!!! Good Luck!");
		}
		if(player.KilledNazi < 250) {
		player.sm("Sorry, you need to kill 250 Nazies before teleporting to the boss.");
		}
		break;[/code]
if the player killed 250+ nazies and click on the portal, he teleport to the boss.
if the player killed less than 250 nazies and click on the portal, it wont teleport and say sorry, you need to kill 250 nazies before teleporting to the boss.

